data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the prestigious Northeastern school district! This charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence sits on a sprawling 1.6-acre lot, providing a serene escape with picturesque views of the Conewago Creek. Step inside and discover a spacious interior featuring a well-appointed kitchen, cozy living areas, and a finished lower level boasting an entertainment area – perfect for hosting gatherings or enjoying movie nights. The lower level also offers potential in-law quarters, adding versatility to this already impressive home.The property doesn't stop impressing there. Outside, a large screened-in porch awaits, offering an ideal spot for relaxation or entertaining guests. Imagine sipping your morning coffee or hosting summer barbecues in this delightful outdoor space.Nature lovers will appreciate the convenience of having direct access to the Conewago Creek. Whether you enjoy fishing, kayaking, or simply floating on the water, this backyard oasis provides endless opportunities for outdoor recreation. For those with hobbies or in need of additional space, an impressive finished outbuilding measuring 39 by 15.3 feet awaits your creative touch. This versatile space can serve as a garage, workshop, studio, or any other purpose you desire. Conveniently located near Highway 83, commuting to and from this residence is a breeze, offering easy access to nearby amenities and attractions. Don't miss the chance to make this Northeastern gem your forever home – where comfort, nature, and convenience come together seamlessly. Schedule your showing today!
